                Please use a CSV file or the standard template to upload Leads.   
                </li>
                <li>You will receive a Email incase is there any Lead Insertion Fails, to your Registered Email Id</li>
                </ul>
                <font color="#FFFF00"> <b><u><apex:commandLink value=" Click here "  action="{!exportToCSV}" title=" Click here " target="_blank"/></u></b></Font> to download the template.  

                </div>
 </apex:form>
 </c:ed_basictemplate>
